#

Sloppy Joe Burger

30 min
$10
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinComfort Food

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

AmericanQuick MealGround Beef

Description

A deliciously messy burger topped with a sweet and tangy Sloppy Joe mix, perfect for a quick and satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • ground beef: 1 lb
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • green bell pepper: 1, chopped
  • sloppy joe sauce: 1 cup
  • burger buns: 4
  • cheese slices (optional): 4
  • pickles (optional): 4 slices
